The paper focuses on image recognition, specifically scene recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a hybrid representation using convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves feature encoding and aggregation, which are common topics in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
